  fresh_kill_pile: ["The fresh-kill pile is reinforced with cool stones, and the Clan cheers the promise of safer, longer-lasting prey.", "New shade over the fresh-kill pile keeps prey fresh, making every hunter's catch feel twice as valuable.", "The completed fresh-kill store smells of clean leaves and abundance, and even the elders praise the clever work."],
